@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tyrsuz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.28) - (v0 + 0.51 + v1 + 0.90)) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.80) / (tmp + 0.81 + v0 + 0.88)))
    v0 = 0.14
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.72)) / ((v1 + 0.98 - v1 + 0.53) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.42)))
    data[tid] = v0
